  "texts": [
    "Convolution-based visual feature extractors (Krizhevsky et al., 2012; Simonyan, 2014; He et al., 2016) were the mainstream of computer vision research for a long time.",
    "In recent years, the Vision Transformer (ViT; Dosovitskiy et al. (2020)) has emerged as a central component in modern VFE systems and has been integrated into numerous multimodal VLMs such as CLIP (Radford et al., 2021).",
    "Although not being the first work that tries to apply Transformers for CV tasks,",
